title: Talkin' Jaco, Miles & More with Vince Wilburn Jr. & Darryl Jones
description:
Drummer Vince Wilburn Jr. (nephew of Miles Davis) and bassist Darryl Jones (Miles Davis, The Rolling Stones, Sting) talk about bass genius Jaco Pastorius' new Resonance Records discovery "Truth, Liberty & Soul - Live in NYC: The Complete 1982 NPR Jazz Alive! Recording," as well as the Miles Electric Band (of which they are both a part of), The Rolling Stones and more!

Truth, Liberty & Soul is Available Now! 
Resonance Records - http://bit.ly/2lOX5sV
Amazon.com - http://amzn.to/2qwNL3u
iTunes - http://apple.co/2p8pm2w (*includes digital booklet download)
